Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Fujinuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're under arrest for murder\Nand attemped murder resulting from arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't end here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still have to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just once more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:00:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I mustered\Nthe courage and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I finished what I had to do early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Right, Hinazuki?\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:01:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to pull it off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:01:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru is a gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't have to be graceful,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I can't have any regrets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because if I fail,\NI'm not getting another chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my final Revival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:42.25,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna get a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just got my allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have\Nokonomiyaki on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah!\N- Nice one, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read that book I lent you\Nthe week before last?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poe's "The Switched Man."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I haven't read it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't remember that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A book he lent me 18 years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The story's really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Read it when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, dinner will be ready in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Satoru?\NDon't just stand there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight with Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mom. Remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is, you can go to Ueno\Nwithout changing trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:09.80,LowSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,February 29th, 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}February 29th, 1988.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The day before Kayo Hinazuki becomes\Nthe first victim of a kidnapping serial killer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the third time I've met this day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru's got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what he said last time,\Nalbeit a day early now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:27.44,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Hockey Club\N1988 National Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm throwing caution\Nto the wind this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I lost the book you lent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, can I talk to you out in the hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, let me say this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Recently... How can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you being serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you used to pretend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even though you didn't care\Nat all about other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did the best you could then,\Nin your own right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I like you better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Except I want an answer\Nto this nagging suspicion I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you've become another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like, another\Npersonality has been added.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I realized you'd changed the day\NI saw you looking at Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd noticed Hinazuki's cuts\Nand bruises a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,looked on from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you addressed the issue\Nright in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a will that said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"This is what you're gonna do"\Nhad possessed your body
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and put me to shame too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a superhero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or, I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're Satoru after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki is going to be murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw where she's physically abused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll stop it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, you don't become a superhero\Nafter achieving results.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You already are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A superhero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you hated Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like how people have an aversion\Nto others similar to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I did hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was also attracted\Nto something about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, Kenya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand in the hallway with those buckets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Superheroes often get\Nthe short end of the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make a stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiromi, Kenya and Hinazuki, will you\Nwait for me at the children's center?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Sure.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MARCH
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomorrow, March 1st,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki will be safe as long as\Nshe isn't left alone at the park.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The problem is March 2nd,\Nthe day of the birthday party.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want Yuuki to have an alibi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki, is your dad's bedroom\Non the first floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Facing the main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just thinking\Nit was probably noisy at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right. One more thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you sometimes see Kayo Hinazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, she's become\Na part of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I haven't seen her\Naround for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best damn possible result!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the first time I'd heard Yuuki\Nuttering something close to a curse word.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-See you, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure the real killer\Nhappened to see him with Hinazuki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and decided then to use him as a patsy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuki, wait for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna prevent the murder\Nfrom ever happening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.39,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHIRAKABA CHILDREN'S CENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki! Kenya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.77,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}February 29th (Monday)\NSatoru, we're in the gym next door!\NKenya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We all came over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Get in on this, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess three people can't play Othello.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't avoid drastic changes like this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be able to make predictions\Nthrough March 2nd.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SATORU & HINAZUKI\NHAPPY BIRTHDAY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru! Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:01.61,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,March 2nd 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}March 1st was X-day\Nand it went just like last time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beginning with my actions today,\NI'm going to change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot something at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something you need right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it looks weird,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this isn't the time\Nto worry about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.26,BigSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll kill you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The coup de grace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This way the police will serve\Nas Yuuki's alibi for tonight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is somebody out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll get her out of the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I keep her away from Hinazuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I just take you out of the picture...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your cool, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be really bad if she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be even worse if you were put away\Nfor it, unable to help anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been following you\Nfor the past two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been desperate to save Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought you'd be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I thought this was the day\NHinazuki was most at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, you did something disturbing\Nbefore coming here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:13:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was to get the police over\Nto that house for another reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided. Kenya, I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the police to stop\Nthat mother's abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru... It could cause quite a stir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought\Nabout how it'll all shake out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya, I just came up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care\Nif I have to commit a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or if I'm caught along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't even care if they lock me up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how it ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anything is better than Hinazuki dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything\Nthat'll get you arrested, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom would be devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think my mom would say "Well done."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I can picture that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm gonna drop Hinazuki off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll clean up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time I didn't forget to bring my jacket\Nand work gloves when I left the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hinazuki...\N- Fujinu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I abduct you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why this is the only\Nthing I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:41.99,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7\NOut of Control
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A retired school bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it was the clubhouse\Nfor Izumi Elementary's ice hockey club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. So you two came.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Are you sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. They got a new bus last year,\Nso this is just used for storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's open the air vents\Nbefore lighting the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's rusted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it obvious\Npeople are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Awesome...\N- Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to live here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although it doesn't have a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Living in a big house\Ndoesn't guarantee happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you, Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now too,\Nbut I'll be back in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll knock three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Satoru, Kenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to thank me.\NWe're friends, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise we'll protect you, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll protect you, Kayo." Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to crawl in a hole\Nwith your line, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"We're friends, Kayo."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It is hard calling her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go with "Hina" instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You call her Kayo, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, there's no need for thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we haven't gotten\Nto the hard part yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if this goes public,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,act like you don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly took a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We stopped somewhere along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and talked about this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a call from Hinazuki's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, no calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving early tomorrow,\Nso you can go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This'll do for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cup noodles in the middle\Nof the night is good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time\NI've had a night like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:18:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning a camping trip with Kenya\Nand the others for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go with us, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get out of here\Nbefore the Izumi Elementary kids come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:35.98,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}March 3rd\N(Thursday){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo is late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}This is the afternoon broadcast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Everyone remember to wash\Nyour hands before lunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has Hinazuki's mother called the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is she hasn't looked for her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last time it was March 2nd,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki got back home before 9:00 PM.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her mother and her mother's\Nboyfriend physically abused her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They shut her up in the shed,\Nbut she disappeared before 11:00 PM.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At 12:30 AM on the 3rd,\NHinazuki's mother called Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just before dawn on the 3rd,\Nthe kidnapper murdered Hinazuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time there are major changes\Nin the actions of Hinazuki, us,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki's mother, and the killer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happens after this\Nis uncharted territory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.29,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STAFF ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gaku Yashiro\Nfrom Mikoto Elementary School.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Kazu or Osamu about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for getting you\Ninvolved, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what form it takes,\NI'm touched that you're counting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even if I went home, no one else\Nwould be there until 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to you too, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shutting you up in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I've never had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I mustered\Nthe courage to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stop by your house\Ntomorrow morning, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother will have no choice\Nbut to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I understand\Nwhat's going on more or less,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but what happens in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I instigated it\Nand you guys then helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...no one will be to blame, right? I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That had been my blind spot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the way home, Kenya said,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I bet you hadn't thought of that, Satoru."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You're right," I answered\Nand continued,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone like that is a hero to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that Satoru?{\i0}
